data.description: ** Seller willing to pay $4,000 in flex money** Come take a look at this spacious home on over half an acre near the Woodlands Golf Course. As you enter in the home you’ll be greeted by beautiful hardwood floors that run throughout the home. It opens up into a spacious family room that takes you to your outside covered and screened in patio area perfect for entertaining. The HVAC and hot water heater are both new and the architectural shingle roof is under 10 years in age. The windows in the home have been updated and you’ll find two new rooms and a bathroom that have been added to the home adding more heated sq footage to this already beautiful home. Home recently appraised, price and sq footage based on appraisal.
